{"tid":1084403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聲優愛好[45] I'm嘅明日之星 本渡楓","createTime":"2019-03-30T11:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T12:24:29.000Z","uid":181228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee6402ca1d4af45f12451172b38105a98997cc9","tid":1084403,"uid":181228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T11:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jtvd06j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjtvd06j.jpg&h=2e90b1c5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n本名:本渡ほんど 楓かえで（Hondo Kaede）<br />\n暱稱 えーでちゃん<br />\n出生 1996年3月6日<br />\n星座 雙魚座<br />\n年齡 23歲<br />\n出身地區 日本愛知縣名古屋<br />\n所屬公司 I'm Enterprise<br />\n出道角色 優香等《青春&times;機關槍》<br />\n代表角色 四葉心《見習神明 秘密的COCOTAMA》<br />\n紺《烏菈菈迷路帖》<br />\n小鳥遊緋雁《亞人醬有話要說》<br />\n衛藤可奈美《刀使之巫女》<br />\n三島瞳《黑社會的超能力女兒》<br />\n源櫻《佐賀偶像是傳奇》<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eb0190n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feb0190n.jpg&h=b11443f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-小時候碰見一位老奶奶說她化了妝很好看，於是產生了「想成為受歡迎的演員」的想法。<br />\n-高中2年級時候進入了日本播音演技研究所名古屋校（同期生有長繩麻理亞）。<br />\n-高中畢業前都沒能在事務所的試音中合格，後來考上大學，但打算正式去做聲優而決定退學。<br />\n-之後在I'm Enterprise協力、名古屋校主辦的名古屋PR企劃的試音選拔中合格。<br />\n2015年4月，正式加入I'm Enterprise，同年出演《青春&times;機關槍》從而聲優出道。<br />\n2019年，在第13屆聲優獎中獲得新人女優賞。<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n喜歡辣的東西，嘗過最辣的食物是名古屋的一家有名的中華料理店「味仙」里的台灣拉麵<br />\n愛犬名叫莉莉<br />\n愛好是看戲劇<br />\n喜歡的運動是游泳和耐久跑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XYqULzh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXYqULzh.png&h=e66dfd62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d10a6836eba6a59f04f199d1b2acde3d70a9f31d","tid":1084403,"uid":181228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WPCPzu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWPCPzu8.jpg&h=2cc681d3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n刀使ノ巫女  刻みし一閃の燈火 1周年記念  イベント"},{"pid":"74c214baf7bb18d5f6527f19ec9c673931112905","tid":1084403,"uid":64143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T11:21:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JeyviWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJeyviWQ.jpg&h=d8d52377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8acbe8c9c982b0aead7cd58c04f3690d18e400e","tid":1084403,"uid":181228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T11:29:15.000Z","msg":"[補充]えーで分別喺刀使巫女同Saga開Live嘅相 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t520Gb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft520Gb3.jpg&h=69e2d458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tqg1qDK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftqg1qDK.jpg&h=9a335eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LD6kGb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLD6kGb4.jpg&h=c45343dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a8a51974475d5cbdb20d3442eb954c6fdc96f31","tid":1084403,"uid":184229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8acbe8c9c982b0aead7cd58c04f3690d18e400e","tid":1084403,"uid":181228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T11:29:15.000Z","msg":"[補充]えーで分別喺刀使巫女同Saga開Live嘅相 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t520Gb3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft520Gb3.jpg&h=69e2d458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tqg1qDK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftqg1qDK.jpg&h=9a335eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LD6kGb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLD6kGb4.jpg&h=c45343dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"好想聽次刀使Live<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"203a554c22d347151a5621b19d203e07f